</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-08-02-0071-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-08-02-0071-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-08-02-0070" class="document">Boucher to GW, 13 June 1768</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-08-02-0071-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-02-08-02-0071-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>Though endowed with an active and wide-ranging mind, Boucher himself had little formal training in the classics.</p>

